  "plot outline": "Texas greenhorn Joe Buck arrives in New York City for the first time. Preening himself as a real \"hustler\", he finds that he is the one getting \"hustled\" until he teams up with down-and-out but resilient outcast Ratso Rizzo. The initial \"country cousin meets city cousin\" relationship deepens. In their efforts to bilk a hostile world rebuffing them at every turn, this unlikely pair progress from partners in shady business to comrades. Each has found his first real friend.",
